data.description: This charming 2021 home features open-concept living, plus the split floorplan provides you with privacy and functionality. The kitchen features granite countertops and the oversized island gives plenty of storage for all your kitchen needs. The owners' suite bathroom boasts a double-sink vanity and a pristine tiled shower. The walk-in closet provides lots of room for your whole wardrobe. Step outside, and you'll find a huge fenced-in yard that's perfect for outdoor entertaining or enjoying the Florida sun! The trussed porch to relax in the shade. This wonderful home also includes a two-car garage, laundry room, and the energy efficiency that comes with a 2 year old home. | Seller is offering $10,000 flex cash to the buyer to use towards closing costs, or rate buydown, Loan is assumable!
